description: BMO ESG US Corporate Bond Hedged to CAD Index ETF has been designed to replicate, to the extent possible, the performance of the Bloomberg MSCI US Corporate Sustainability SRI Index, net of expenses. Securities held in the Index are a variety of investment grade corporate bonds issued in the U.S. in U.S. dollars, which have a term to maturity greater than one year, and have a higher MSCI ESG rating than their peers.
name: BMO ESG US Corporate Bond Hedged to CAD Index ETF
